    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the grill to high</p><p>Slice your<strong> portobello mushrooms</strong> finely</p><p>Peel and finely slice your<strong> brown onion[s]</strong></p>",
            "order": 1
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>sliced mushroom </strong>and <strong>sliced onion </strong>to a bowl with your <strong>ground paprika, toasted sesame seeds</strong>, a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>sugar </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up then and add them to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray</p><p>Put the tray under the grill for 15-20 min, turning once halfway, or until slightly charred \u2013 these are your <strong>smoky mushrooms</strong></p>",
            "order": 2
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
            "order": 3
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add a knob of <strong>butter </strong>to a pot with a lid</p><p>Once melted, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> and your <strong>miso</strong></p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
            "order": 4
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>basmati rice </strong>and 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[325ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>to the pot and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once cooked, remove from the heat and keep covered until serving \u2013 this is your <strong>miso butter rice</strong></p>",
            "order": 5
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Boil a kettle</p>",
            "order": 6
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once every thing is ready, boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>pho broth paste </strong>and <strong>toasted sesame oil </strong>to a jug with 200ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [250ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and a squeeze of <strong>lime </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>fragrant broth</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
            "order": 7
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>miso butter rice </strong>in bowls with the <strong>smoky mushrooms </strong>on top</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Pour over the <strong>fragrant broth</strong></p><p>Garnish with your <strong>crispy onions</strong>, <strong>chopped coriander </strong>and a wedge of <strong>lime</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
